 />\n當有樓既 樓價下跌 影響到佢地<br />\n佢地會出黎屌示威者<br />\n當721 佢地仔女受傷 佢地會出黎屌黑警<br />\n我地要做既係<br />\n引發更多人抗議反抗<br />\n光環？道德高地？係極權暴政下有咩用<br />\n睇下黑警用咩手段拘捕<br />\n嬲？可以形容到？<br />\n與其日日外國頭條<br />\n不如自己香港自己救<br />\n<br />\n屌你勇武柒頭 入撚哂黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451318</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"76213889649660e5f981120a94c1fe7cd6014f01","tid":1448193,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:47:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以眼還眼 黑警死全家！<br />\n心態改變命運<br />\n人數決定一切<br />\n<br />\n你 班 仆 街 幾 時 先 肯 無 限 期 四 罷？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450867</a><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"f41dbb9257ffad9adf3eb6dc8bd0b0384b888f15","tid":1448193,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:53:25.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"c3f2679ea8b23f0be88fded60a476d398f6bab55","tid":1448193,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:54:55.000Z","msg":"大貨車"},{"pid":"b0aa83f9f32dec4b1819120f9204aa30ac0af670","tid":1448193,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:55:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22ed924977092efaa08b054798e5c491bc2105f2","tid":1448193,"uid":135840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:55:45.000Z","msg":"食狗肉都唔割！"},{"pid":"623905cdd745fe70e815b4e0fac7fcccb3245249","tid":1448193,"uid":202772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:57:06.000Z","msg":"攞刀啦仲打拳頭交咩"},{"pid":"ea79f92d05da4a27e64882a0ffb8021c3cb5488d","tid":1448193,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:59:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"182bfd1df2d961fdf2f8800f0b43562d90a2ca89","tid":1448193,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:59:50.000Z","msg":"全民機場<