ike":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc5a62fc03ff4857f374c93245c00cc6602d80e0","tid":1448193,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:03:24.000Z","msg":"你不如教埋大家<br />\n如果遇到長電梯<br />\n點樣走？點樣走得快？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:32:20.000Z","msg":"無得走得快，只係後排嘅人守後揾野擋子彈比前排嘅人走先，唔可以一大堆人沖入電梯，亦唔可以比警犬太快撲到入電梯，啲警犬係會拉人出黎打，只要人夠多同識反抗，佢地係唔會亂咁衝前揾棍打人，因為佢地是但一個比人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拉入人群就可以比人私了</span></span><br />\n<br />\n電梯個capcity本身太低，一比警犬入到去佢地就最少可以攬炒，佢地實會贏，最好就唔去搭電梯，但係尋日嘅位置其實無得走，無得唔揀電梯，亦都無野可以擋到子彈，但係可以近戰脅持警犬嘅機會就大把，識做啦大家"},{"pid":"ec99af61d89816fc16b158987fc8219ecbc45bd5","tid":1448193,"uid":63298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"太古嗰下，冇人舉背囊擋子彈，就算冇手盾都要用袋啦，俾人係咁射就冇人會反抗到"},{"pid":"bd4c6b95d1e18d455acf748e26082d27cf63ef0e","tid":1448193,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce2671c636f767b175a71a6ebad4288067e7ed4","tid":1448193,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"請抱著想殺死對方的心去打"},{"pid":"5f25be7b3be194a19093dbd228f7a9d517b3bdcc","ti